        bindings = <
&none  &kp LS(N1)  &none  &none  &none  &none  &kp N6  &kp N7  &kp N8  &kp N9  &percent_pipe_td  &none
&none  &td250 LS(N7) LS(N2)  &kp SEMI  &kp F3  &kp F10  &kp F11  &kp LS(N3)  &kp N4  &kp N5  &kp N6  &minus_slash  &none
